Title: The Kun-Lai Kicker
Description:
Have you ever seen the Brewmoon Festival?

The good folks of Binan Village host quite a party. And tonight's festivities are brew-catered by none other than yours truly here.

I am making my famous Kun-Lai Kicker!

Think you might come and join us for the festivities? It should be a completely relaxing event with absolutely no danger whatsoever.
